\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces AquaVolt-AI Decoupled Stress Identification Pipeline. Multi-source satellite data streams (Sentinel-2, ECOSTRESS, ERA5-Land, MODIS) are spatially fused into an 8$\times $8 sub-field sector grid. The Physics-Informed Machine Learning (PIML) residual architecture applies FAO-56 physical constraints to compute water balance variables ($D_r$, RAW, $K_s$) and atmospheric demand (VPD, $\Delta T$). The DSI Classification Engine assigns each sector-hour to one of four stress categories, and the DSI Gating Logic controls the final irrigation trigger.}}{9}{figure.caption.1}\protected@file@percent }
\providecommand*\caption@xref[2]{\@setref\relax\@undefined{#1}}
\newlabel{fig:methodology}{{1}{9}{AquaVolt-AI Decoupled Stress Identification Pipeline. Multi-source satellite data streams (Sentinel-2, ECOSTRESS, ERA5-Land, MODIS) are spatially fused into an 8$\times $8 sub-field sector grid. The Physics-Informed Machine Learning (PIML) residual architecture applies FAO-56 physical constraints to compute water balance variables ($D_r$, RAW, $K_s$) and atmospheric demand (VPD, $\Delta T$). The DSI Classification Engine assigns each sector-hour to one of four stress categories, and the DSI Gating Logic controls the final irrigation trigger}{figure.caption.1}{}}
